      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ASA 1 or 2 volunteers

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  digestive diseases, gastroparesis

          -  Smokers

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Diabetes Mellitus

          -  Medication affecting gastric motility

          -  Previous gastrointestinal surgery
      </textblock>
